items.description:
Spectacular day to my 77 glorious followers, I am back from my short hiatus and the excellent news is that after more than a week I managed to fix the driver issue and now my GPU is back in operation. I rushed to get some testing done now that my ass cpu renders are out of question and because im going to be very busy the next few days and I thought I shouldnt keep you guys waiting for 2 weeks for another Lora. I still have to try getting CoreCtrl working since my gpu is stuck in balanced mode so its only doing 4s/it instead of 2.4 but that can wait. I also set up a google form for requests, which can be any character or concept of course within reason, so here is the link if you want to request dont be shy. Apart from that we hit 600 favourites and 2.1k downloads, which im not sure how much more that is since last time but its still an achievement nonetheless :D.

Anyways I have created Una as per last voting session, I havent had much time to test since its getting late already, but I trained her on all the event pics and her outfit as well so she is easily customized.
